description: Nonzero coefficients in theta series of {E_7}* lattice.
comments: In the Eichler and Zagier reference this is e_4(A014601(n)), n >= 0, (p. 141), where e_4 is obtained from e_{4,1}(n,r), eq. (7), p. 22, depending only on 4*n-r^2 >= 0 (for integers n and r), i.e. on A014601(n), n >= 0 (with a new notation for n). - _Wolfdieter Lang_, Jan 08 2016
references: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 125.
M. Eichler and D. Zagier, The Theory of Jacobi Forms, Birkh√§user, 1985, p. 141.
links: N. Elkies and B. H. Gross, Embeddings into the integral octonions, Olga Taussky-Todd: in memoriam, Pacific J. Math. 1997, Special Issue, 147-158.
